projects.description:
Developer, author, speaker at online courses. 
Theme – pitching of technical and scientific projects.

- Author and speaker at online courses for Moscow Institute of Physics and Technology (https://mipt.ru/english/) 

- Author and speaker of Coursera “Presentation of Technological Projects” (Russian language)

- Author and speaker at online courses about pitching of technological projects for National Technological Initiative NTI2035 (https://nti2035.ru).

- Author and speaker at online courses for MTS (http://ir.mts.ru/home/default.aspx).

- Author and speaker at online courses for Rusnano (https://en.rusnano.com/).

As a course author, I performed the following tasks:
- Creating a work plan;
- Development of the course program;
- Creating assignments for online course participants: tests and other assignments;
- Recording videos on the topics of the course;
- My online courses were on the topics of corporate sales and presenting business projects to a given; target audience (clients, investors, partners).
